{"tid":2276852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保護傘下周重開：打擊令我們更茁壯","createTime":"2020-11-08T05:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T05:34:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb27e52716447315fef817ae4957a9578613124a","tid":2276852,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:31:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/2SYVI252LBEGXL6KSKH7XIMGUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2F2SYVI252LBEGXL6KSKH7XIMGUE%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft26tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=9c2b2f68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2F2SYVI252LBEGXL6KSKH7XIMGUE%2F&h=36cc6f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/2SYVI252LBEGXL6KSKH7XIMGUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保護傘下周重開：打擊令我們更茁壯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jS1rutygKfWUUFDJ_OO5aopZUYE=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3YO62KPOZVEUNJBZZ7F4FFFEC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjS1rutygKfWUUFDJ_OO5aopZUYE%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3YO62KPOZVEUNJBZZ7F4FFFEC4.jpg&h=ba1d94a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■保護傘昨晚於fb宣佈下周三恢復營業。<br />\n<br />\n協助在台尋求庇護港人維持生計的保護傘餐廳，上月16日遭潑糞而停業三周，保護傘昨晚於fb宣佈下周三恢復營業，並強調：「打擊只會令我們更茁壯，威嚇使我們更昂首向前」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n停業期間如常支薪<br />\n<br />\n保護傘fb寫道：「停業三星期，全職和兼職手足同事均回店協助清冼；被污染的爐具，廚櫃和餐具，全部更換；被破壞的牆壁重新粉飾。停業期間，手足的支援毫無間斷，員工的薪酬如常支付。」保護傘並在文末表示：「平坦大道，港人萬眾一心攜手前行。現在四野荊途，縱前路模糊不清，只要堅持信念無忘初心，雖攀山涉水披荊斬棘，又何懼繼續前行。香港加油！」<br />\n<br />\n由香港律師黃國桐發起、讓流亡到台灣的手足在當地工作的餐廳保護傘今年4月16日正式開幕，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"6253d63deb8c97953cd168780aaca8bfe328e86b","tid":2276852,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"下次去台灣, 如果順路的話, 一定幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879485bbb945586b64e1dc35a5e74965a118cb69","tid":2276852,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"對比光時p 小姐係度飲人血...呢間真係做得好好多"}]}